title: Plagiostropha roseopinna
text:
Plagiostropha roseopinna is a <a href="species">species</a> of <a href="sea%20snail">sea snail</a>, a marine <a href="gastropod">gastropod</a> <a href="mollusk">mollusk</a> in the <a href="family%20%28biology%29">family</a> <a href="Drilliidae">Drilliidae</a>.
Description.
The length of the shell varies between 6 mm and 14 mm.
Distribution.
This marine species occurs off <a href="Mactan%20Island">Mactan Island</a>, Cebu, the Philippines.
